'''Todd Demong''' is a [[Wikipedia:Canadian|Canadian]] artist<ref name="Linkedin" /> who pencilled the [[Star Wars comic books|comic]] story "[[Number Two in the Galaxy]]" for [[Dark Horse Comics]], which featured in the [[Star Wars Tales 18|eighteenth issue]] of the ''[[Star Wars Tales]]'' comic series,<ref name="No2" /> published on [[December 24]], [[2003]].<ref name="Tales18date">{{DarkHorse|url=Comics/12-577/Star-Wars-Tales-18|text=Star Wars Tales #18}}</ref>

